<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Enzian von Bibra</head><p>Der Rat teilt Unkenntnis wegen einer angeblichen Bitte aus Straßburg zur Anwerbung von Söldnern mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l17">Encʒıan von Bıbra </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l18"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Encʒıan als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe Jr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> habt daʒ vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l19">~ dıe von Straſburg <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchriben</expan> vnd gebetten ſüllen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> Jn leẅte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l20">ʒu beſtellen vmb Jr gelt etc / das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l21">vns / dauon niht wıſſend / noch von den von Straſburg darumb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_line_1577277901554_1452"><expan>verſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> noch befolhen . Denn do wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l24"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> gallȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Enczian von Bibra</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Enczian, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> habt, daz uns die von
                        Strasburg <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schriben</expan> und gebetten süllen
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, in lewte zu bestellen umb ir gelt
                        etc., das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und ist uns davon
                        niht wissend, noch von den von Strasburg darumb
                            <expan>verschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> noch befolhen. Denn do wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Galli.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
